<h3> &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp About Us </h3>

<p>&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp  Prolet Inc. is one of Canada`s premier staffing companies with a focus on technical personnel and engineering <br> &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp services  for  the Canadian power generation and nuclear industry. Our company is run by experienced nuclear <br> &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp engineers with a consulting background and extensive management experience. We also offer experienced <br> &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp communications group for writing, editing and documentation control. An experienced but a relatively young and <br> &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp lean company, Prolet has been  providing services to the Canadian public and private sector since 1999.</p>

<img class = "align-right"  src = "assets/images/brain.jpg" width="300" height="200" alt="Success" align="right"><br>

<h3> &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp Our Services </h3>

<ul> 
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp<li> Staffing services - Prolet Inc. provides a full range of staffing and placement services for Employers seeking qualified technical personnel. Professionals seeking job opportunities benefit from Prolet`s extensive experience in the staffing industry.   </li>
<li> Engineering consulting - engineering support services to the power industry, with an emphasis on nuclear power reactors. </li>
<li> Communications - communication support services including writing, editing, proofreading, translation and document preparation.</li>
</ul>

